A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing April 2025 as Arab American Heritage Month; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, for over a century, Arab Americans have been making valuable contributions
3 to several aspects of American society, including medicine, law, business, education,
4 technology, government, military service, and culture; and
5 WHEREAS, since migrating to America, men and women of Arab descent have shared their
6 rich culture and traditions with neighbors and friends while also setting fine examples of
7 model citizens and public servants; and
8 WHEREAS, Arab Americans have brought their resilient family values, strong work ethic,
9 dedication to education, and diversity in faith and creed to America, adding strength to our
10 great democracy; and
11 WHEREAS, Arab Americans have enriched American society by sharing in the
12 entrepreneurial spirit that makes our nation free and prosperous, and they join all Americans
13 in the desire to see a peaceful and diverse society where every individual is treated equally
14 and feels safe; and
