15 WHEREAS, the incredible contributions and heritage of Arab Americans have helped build
16 a better nation, and the State of Georgia is proud of its many Arab American citizens who
17 contribute so much to their communities as neighbors, coworkers, and friends.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
19 recognize April 2025 as Arab American Heritage Month.
20 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
21 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the public and the
22 press.
